{"tid":810051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Elon Musk 於網台節目隊草後 Tesla 股價大跌","createTime":"2018-09-07T15:48:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-08T00:52:54.000Z","uid":23122,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"263482c0e64b82b491ca5fd36fdd9415b901f799","tid":810051,"uid":23122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T15:48:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2018/sep/07/tesla-chief-elon-musk-smokes-marijuana-on-live-web-show\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2018%2Fsep%2F07%2Ftesla-chief-elon-musk-smokes-marijuana-on-live-web-show&d=LACzl6Du%2FRWIbUjHR75B0%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=5b87c48d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.theguardian.com/technology/2018/sep/07/tesla-chief-elon-musk-smokes-marijuana-on-live-web-show</a><br />\n<br />\n香港01 有中文版<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ：<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/財經快訊/232935/馬斯克於網台節目吸大麻-tesla股價早段曾插逾1成\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A%2F232935%2F%E9%A6%AC%E6%96%AF%E5%85%8B%E6%96%BC%E7%B6%B2%E5%8F%B0%E7%AF%80%E7%9B%AE%E5%90%B8%E5%A4%A7%E9%BA%BB-tesla%E8%82%A1%E5%83%B9%E6%97%A9%E6%AE%B5%E6%9B%BE%E6%8F%92%E9%80%BE1%E6%88%90&d=LACzl6Du%2FRWIbUjHR75B0%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=4c53ce79\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/財經快訊/232935/馬斯克於網台節目吸大麻-tesla股價早段曾插逾1成</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>Tesla shares crash after Elon Musk smokes joint on live web show<br />\nTwo senior executives quit electric carmaker as market value falls 8%</strong></span><br />\n<br />\nJulia Carrie Wong<br />\nFirst published on Fri 7 Sep 2018 13.26 BST<br />\nTesla shares crashed 8% on Friday as two of its senior executives quit, just hours after the electric carmaker&rsquo;s chief executive Elon Musk sparked concern by smoking marijuana on a live web show.<br />\n<br />\nThe company&rsquo;s head of accounting, Dave Morton, and head of human resources, Gaby Toledano, said they were leaving the company, which has been placed at the centre of a string of controversies by its maverick CEO.<br />\n<br />\nMorton, who joined the company just one month ago, said he was leaving because &ldquo;the level of public attention placed on the company, as well as the pace within the company, have exceeded my expectations&rdquo;.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;This caused me to reconsider my future. I want to be clear that I believe strongly in Tesla, its mission and its future prospects, and I have no disagreements with Tesla&rsquo;s leadership or its financial reporting.&rdquo;"},{"pid":"32fdce2fd95cb3443fb0ac4773a34fc98fc50aa8","tid":810051,"uid":106426,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:02:24.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e29a4917083083010d905839c49b8d0d921afda6","tid":810051,"uid":123264,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:03:18.000Z","msg":"又有人做佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47dcf1d40e417bf947777a440db2232fd6a60e36","tid":810051,"uid":20414,"like":99,"dislike":4,"score":95,"quote":{"pid":"e29a4917083083010d905839c49b8d0d921afda6","tid":810051,"uid":123264,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:03:18.000Z","msg":"又有人做佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:05:07.000Z","msg":"佢自己白痴關人咩事<br />\n咩身份呀大佬，已經俾人屌唔識管理，仲公開隊草"},{"pid":"a3a115926f6fca529e80d9c5c6ec3fc8b2ff01aa","tid":810051,"uid":2507,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-07T16:10:12.000Z","msg":"電動飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" clas